{"Id":489,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-muhammadmakin","Author":"Muhammad Makin","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://quranenc.com/check/chinese_makin/v1.0.0-csv.1 , https://quranenc.com/en/browse/chinese_makin , https://quranenc.com ,","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":98,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他们在他们的主那里的报酬是下临诸河的常住的乐园，他们将永居其中，安拉喜悦他们，他们喜悦安拉；这是畏惧安拉者所有的。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"当大地猛烈地震动，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"抛其重担，"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"人们说：“大地怎么啦？”"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"在那日，大地将报告它的消息。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"因为你的主已启示了它；"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"在那日，人们将纷纷地离散，以便他们得见自己行为的报应。"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"行一个小蚂蚁重的善事者，将见其报酬；"},{"SurahNumber":99,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"作一个小蚂蚁重的恶事者，也将见其恶报。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以喘息而奔驰的马队盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"以蹄发火花的马队盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"以早晨出击，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"卷起尘埃，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"攻入敌围的马队盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"人对于主, 确是孤负的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"他自己对那孤负确是见证的，"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他对于财产确是酷好的。"},{"SurahNumber":100,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"难道他不知道吗？当坟中的朽骨被揭发，"}]}